channel.title: [RS2] Alchemy - Both Low And High, NO Colors And Easy Setup
channel.description:
well i was looking through some of my old scripts because i was looking for a high alcher. i didnt seem to find one that would work to good anymore so i decided to make my own. i hope everyone enjoys it and uses it as much as they want. the only thing that i ask is for you to give me some feedback on it. thanxs :) ~~Pmh~~
Also: Here Is A Progress Report Of A Little Test Run I Did :P
Pmh1000's High Alcher ++++++++++++++++++++++++ Currently: Alched All Items Worked For 1 Hours, 17 Minutes and 3 Seconds Alched 500 Items Gold Gained: 384000 About 200 Items Before Random Log Only 0 Alches Left
PROGRESS REPORT WITH VERSION 2.0!
Pmh1000's High Alcher V 2.0 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ Currently: Casting High Alch Worked For 5 Hours, 50 Minutes and 10 Seconds Alched 1999 Items Gold Gained: 1535232 About 30 Items B4 Random Log Only 1 Alches Left Took 10, 10-15 Min Breaks
[size=18pt]UPDATES!!: 1) Fixed The CheckNats Procedure So Now It WIll Detect If You Are Out Of Nats 2) Fixed The Login/LogOut Problem 3) Added In FORMS!!!!! HopeFully That Will Make The Setup Easier :D 4) Fixed The Little Label Error Thing 5) Complete Remake, Works With Divi And Added Lots Of Cool New Stuff, Check It Out In Version 2.0! [/size]
Pic Of The Form :P [IMG]http://img117.imageshack.us/img117/8594/alcherformbo5.png[/img]
Currently [size=24pt][font=Chiller][color=blue]336[/color][/size] People Have DownLoaded This Script :P + The Number On The Attachment

item.title: [RS2] Alchemy - Both Low And High, NO Colors And Easy Setup
item.dc:creator: @the_scar_noob the scar noob
item.description:
@the_scar_noob wrote:

To make it compile do this:

  1. Add this line to the vars:
    Label1, Label2, Label3, Label4, Label5, Label6 :TLabel;
  2. you’ll get another error:
    Line 734: [Error] (19462:11): Duplicate identifier ‘SHOWFORM’ in script
    just give it another name and go to the mainloop (line 743+), go to ± line 745 and the thing you changed (for example i called it ShowFormm;) place that were the ShowForm; is (i just added a “m”)
    Than it’ll compile

The Scar Noob.
